  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As an action, you can reach into your Alchemist's Satchel and pullout a flask of neon colored brew, and hurl it at a creature or object within 30 feet of you. The flask shatters on impact. You always know the direction to the target of the brew as long as it is on the same plane as you. Creatures within 30 feet of the target ignore the invisible condition effecting it. This effect lasts until you dismiss it (no action required) or until you use this brew on another creature or object. Your effect can be dispelled with dispel magic, and is treated as a spell with a level equal to half your artificer level (maximum 9th level).</p>",
